channel.title: [help] how to change home on deltascape [help]
channel.description: how do i change my home from falador to edgeville, and how can i change the coords for the home tele? PLEASE help me :(

item.title: [help] how to change home on deltascape [help]
item.dc:creator: @adamhelloman8 adamhelloman8
item.description:
@adamhelloman8 wrote:

Open up player.java

search (ctrl + f)

initial x and y coordinates of the player

underneath it, you will see

heightLevel = 0
toX = ####;
toY = ####;

Well your number signs will be the coords for fally, but replace them with where you want your new starting place to be.
